frus:attachment.p:
(102) Max Winkelhausen.—Born at Danzig, Prussia,
                            March 14, 1856; emigrated May 7, 1876, when twenty years of age;
                            naturalized August 28, 1882.

(109) Peter B. Brodersen.—Born at Klintum, island
                            of Föhr, Germany, September 13, 1855; emigrated March 28, 1873;
                            naturalized June 18, 1880.
